  "description": "This image captures a majestic waterfall cascading down a steep, rocky cliff face, partially obscured by a dense forest of tall, slender evergreen trees. The waterfall appears as a bright white streak against the darker tones of the rock and foliage, creating a strong contrast. The trees, primarily pine or fir, frame the view and create a sense of depth. Sunlight filters through the branches, illuminating parts of the forest and cliff. The overall composition is vertical and emphasizes the height and scale of the natural landscape.",
